- git clone git://git.alech.de/voicebarf.git
- Edit components/voicebarf/ami.yml to match your /etc/asterisk/manager.conf
- mkdir /usr/share/asterisks/sounds/voicebarf
  Link generic to voicebarf/voice/generic
  Create audio content for conference/ event/ room/ and speaker/ directories
- sqlite reminders.sqlite < setup.sqlite (gem install sqlite3-ruby)
